name: Hege
description: Hege is on a quest to become a successful meme in order to win the heart of his crush, Hegena. Join the $HEGE-fund to help turn Hege's dream into reality! The Hege story features 10 chapters, that are unlocked at various market cap goals, ranging from $1m-$1b. NFT's, airdrops, rewards and more are also unlocked at the release of every chapter!
